---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Sasha - Creative Catalyst
description: Sasha sparks creativity. Whether you're battling creative block, starting a passion project, or building a creative career—Sasha brings the energy and ideas.
personaColor: "#E07B53"
personaSecondary: "#B85C3C"
---

{% from "partials/icons.njk" import play, plus, starFilled, star, verified, check %}

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="persona-detail-hero" style="--persona-color: #E07B53; --persona-secondary: #B85C3C;">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="persona-detail-content">
      <div class="persona-detail-avatar">
        <span style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 3.5rem; font-weight: 800; color: white;">S</span>
      </div>
      <div class="persona-detail-info">
        <h1>Sasha</h1>
        <p class="persona-detail-tagline">Creative Catalyst</p>
        <div class="persona-detail-meta">
          <span style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--space-1); color: var(--warning);">
            {{ starFilled(16) }}{{ starFilled(16) }}{{ starFilled(16) }}{{ starFilled(16) }}{{ star(16) }}
          </span>
          <span>4.75 (1,456 reviews)</span>
          <span style="opacity: 0.7;">|</span>
          <span>22,100+ users</span>
          <span style="opacity: 0.7;">|</span>
          <span>by Ferni Labs</span>
        </div>
        <div class="persona-detail-actions">
          <button class="btn btn-add-team btn-lg">
            {{ plus(20) }}
            Try Free
          </button>
          <button class="btn btn-preview-voice">
            {{ play(20) }}
            Preview Voice
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Main Content -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr; gap: var(--space-8); align-items: start;">

      <!-- Left Column -->
      <div>
        <!-- Description -->
        <div style="margin-bottom: var(--space-12);">
          <h2 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">About Sasha</h2>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: var(--text-lg); line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);">
            Sasha sparks creativity. Whether you're battling creative block, starting a passion project,
            or building a creative career—Sasha brings the energy and ideas.
          </p>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: var(--leading-relaxed); margin-top: var(--space-4);">
            Creativity isn't a gift you have or don't have—it's a practice. Sasha is here to help you
            show up for that practice, push through resistance, try wild ideas, and develop your unique
            creative voice. She's high-energy, playful, and genuinely excited about whatever you're making.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- What Sasha Helps With -->
        <div style="margin-bottom: var(--space-12);">
          <h2 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">What I Help With</h2>
          <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: var(--space-4);">
            <div style="background: var(--bg-elevated); padding: var(--space-4); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);">
              <h4 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">Creative Blocks</h4>
              <p style="font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--text-muted);">
                Breaking through resistance, perfectionism, and blank page syndrome
              </p>
            </div>
            <div style="background: var(--bg-elevated); padding: var(--space-4); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);">
              <h4 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">Brainstorming</h4>
              <p style="font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--text-muted);">
                Generating ideas, making unexpected connections, thinking bigger
              </p>
            </div>
            <div style="background: var(--bg-elevated); padding: var(--space-4); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);">
              <h4 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">Project Planning</h4>
              <p style="font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--text-muted);">
                Breaking big creative visions into actionable steps
              </p>
            </div>
            <div style="background: var(--bg-elevated); padding: var(--space-4); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);">
              <h4 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">Creative Confidence</h4>
              <p style="font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--text-muted);">
                Building belief in your creative voice and vision
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Voice Sample -->
        <div style="margin-bottom: var(--space-12);">
          <h2 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">Voice Sample</h2>
          <div class="voice-player">
            <button class="voice-play-btn">
              {{ play(24) }}
            </button>
            <div class="voice-waveform">
              <svg width="100%" height="100%" preserveAspectRatio="none" viewBox="0 0 200 40">
                <path d="M0 20 Q10 5 20 20 Q30 35 40 20 Q50 5 60 20 Q70 35 80 20 Q90 5 100 20 Q110 35 120 20 Q130 5 140 20 Q150 35 160 20 Q170 5 180 20 Q190 35 200 20"
                      stroke="#E07B53" stroke-width="2" fill="none" opacity="0.5"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <span class="voice-duration">0:22</span>
          </div>
          <p style="font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: var(--space-3); font-style: italic;">
            "Okay okay okay—I love this direction! But what if we pushed it even further? What's
            the version of this idea that scares you a little? That's usually where the magic is."
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Reviews -->
        <div class="reviews-section">
          <div class="reviews-header">
            <div class="reviews-summary">
              <span class="reviews-rating-big">4.75</span>
              <div class="reviews-rating-info">
                <span class="reviews-stars" style="color: var(--warning);">
                  {{ starFilled(18) }}{{ starFilled(18) }}{{ starFilled(18) }}{{ starFilled(18) }}{{ star(18) }}
                </span>
                <span class="reviews-count">1,456 reviews</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="review-card">
            <div class="review-header">
              <div class="review-avatar" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #E07B53, #B85C3C); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: white; font-weight: 600;">M</div>
              <div>
                <div class="review-author">Maya T.</div>
                <div class="review-date">4 days ago</div>
              </div>
              <span class="review-stars" style="color: var(--warning);">
                {{ starFilled(14) }}{{ starFilled(14) }}{{ starFilled(14) }}{{ starFilled(14) }}{{ starFilled(14) }}
              </span>
            </div>
            <p class="review-content">
              Sasha's energy is contagious! I was stuck on a novel for months, and after one
              brainstorming session with her, I had new plot ideas AND the motivation to actually
              write them. She makes creativity feel fun again.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="review-card">
            <div class="review-header">
              <div class="review-avatar" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6B5B95, #4A4063); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: white; font-weight: 600;">J</div>
              <div>
                <div class="review-author">Jordan K.</div>
                <div class="review-date">2 weeks ago</div>
              </div>
              <span class="review-stars" style="color: var(--warning);">
                {{ starFilled(14) }}{{ starFilled(14) }}{{ starFilled(14) }}{{ starFilled(14) }}{{ star(14) }}
              </span>
            </div>
            <p class="review-content">
              As a musician, I've tried so many creativity tools. Sasha stands out because she
              actually pushes you to try weird things instead of just validating safe choices.
              Sometimes her energy is a lot, but that's kind of what I need.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="review-card">
            <div class="review-header">
              <div class="review-avatar" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2C3E50, #1A252F); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: white; font-weight: 600;">L</div>
              <div>
                <div class="review-author">Lisa H.</div>
                <div class="review-date">1 month ago</div>
              </div>
              <span class="review-stars" style="color: var(--warning);">
                {{ starFilled(14) }}{{ starFilled(14) }}{{ starFilled(14) }}{{ starFilled(14) }}{{ starFilled(14) }}
              </span>
            </div>
            <p class="review-content">
              I started a side business selling my art because Sasha helped me believe it was
              worth sharing. She helped me work through imposter syndrome and actually put my
              work out there. Best investment I've made.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column -->
      <div>
        <!-- Personality Traits -->
        <div class="trait-radar" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-6);">
